    <div id="process" class="banner">
        <div class="container">
			<h2>What is Eduity?</h2>
			<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2"><p>So much money and time is spent finding employees and jobs. Yet, too many employers have unfilled jobs&mdash;often, <i>great</i> jobs&mdash;and too many people are unemployed, under-employed, and stuck doing meaningless, mindless work. We can collectively solve this problem; we just need a better way to work together. That&rsquo;s what Eduity is: a social platform to guide and support development, so everyone gets the capabilities they need to succeed.</p>  </div>
        </div>
