                <div class="col-sm-6 animated hiding" data-animation="fadeInRight">
					<br/><br/>
                    <article>
                        <h3>A CAPABILITIES <span class="highlight">MAPPING</span> TOOL</h3>
                        <div class="sub-title">Get the Big Picture and Deep Details</div>
                        <p>Eduity makes it easy for employers to map work functions, forecast employment, and get feedback from experts from the corner office to the shop floor. Then Eduity aggregates the data to provide meaningful, useful insights. Each map adds to a complete, comprehensive map of where workforce demand is going tomorrows, as well as what&rsquo;s needed today.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>

                <hr class="clearfix" />

                

