			<h2>What Eduity Can Do for You</h2>
			<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2"><p>Eduity is currently in pilot, and moving toward an initial product. As a fully developed product, Eduity will connect resources to workforce priorities, enable people to proactively meet workforce demand, and provide critical capabilities to employers just-in-time.</p>
<p>To get there, we need your input and feedback. Try us out, input your data, let us know how we can improve. It's a small, upfront investment with potentially huge benefits—for your company, your workforce, and your economy.</p></div>

